            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "All activation foils were enclosed by a cadmium sphere",
                "with 0.10 cm thickness and diameter is 30.0 cm.",
                "Activation foils with thickness up to 1 mm (except the",
                "Manganese foils) were put into a special low-mass",
                "aluminum holder.",
                "130Te, 128Te, 56Fe and 54Fe isotopic foils were",
                "wrapped by aluminum wire and attached to the aluminum",
                "ending of flexo-rabbit to maximize the flux for these",
                "very high-threshold reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " ORTEC GEM35P4"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Correction factor was determined by MCNP6 calculation",
                "and represents spectral shift, flux loss and",
                "self-shielding together."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The experimental uncertainty includes",
                "1. The counting rate uncertainties in HPGe detector,",
                "2. The detector efficiency uncertainty,",
                "3. Uncertainties in the sample position",
                "   during irradiation,",
                "4. Uncertainties in the position of the 252Cf(sf)",
